statements: SELECT * FROM access_control_logs;
SELECT log_id, entry_time FROM access_control_logs ORDER BY entry_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM access_control_logs WHERE entry_time >= '2022-01-01' AND exit_time IS NULL;
SELECT log_id, entry_time, exit_time FROM access_control_logs WHERE exit_time IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM access_control_logs ORDER BY log_id ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM access_control_logs WHERE entry_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT log_id, entry_time FROM access_control_logs WHERE exit_time IS NULL ORDER BY entry_time DESC;
SELECT AVG(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (exit_time - entry_time))) / 3600 AS duration_hours FROM access_control_logs;
SELECT log_id, entry_time, COALESCE(exit_time, 'N/A') AS exit_time_status FROM access_control_logs ORDER BY log_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT COUNT(log_id) AS total_logs, MIN(entry_time) AS first_entry, MAX(exit_time) AS last_exit FROM access_control_logs;
